summary: Ever wanted to marry a hagraven? If so this mod is for you.
descriptionHtml:
I was looking around the nexus to see if anyone had made a mod like this and much to my surprise no one has, which is why I felt it was my duty to bring you all this mod.

[color=#6fa8dc][size=5][b][u]Mod description:[/u][/b][/size][/color]
This mod adds a hagraven named Agnes to the Alchemist's shack south of Ivarstead that all you lucky guys or gals can marry. Agnes uses the female shrill voice.
author: DimesnionLord1
